{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_04_01_short",
  "title": "miho 1話 あ、ヤドカリ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}さんに\nご相談したいことがあるのですが、よろしいですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-san‚\nI have something I want to discuss with you‚ is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9856826626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……めずらしいですね、mihoさんが俺に改まって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's unusual‚ miho-san‚ talking to me so formally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5866665523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "別に大したことではありません\n今度私達が出演する、生放送のバラエティのことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nothing major.\nIt's about the live variety show we will be appearing on soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.68163263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ロケ地には、前日の午後に移動する予定でしたが……\n私だけ、早めにそちらに行かせてほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were scheduled to move to the shooting location the afternoon before…\nBut I want to go there earlier by myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.78163263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "他の仕事のスケジュールはこちらで調整します\n構いませんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll adjust my other work schedules accordingly.\nIs that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3954396825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは構いませんけど……\nなんでまた、いきなり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's fine‚ but…\nWhy so suddenly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "当日は、海辺の特設セットで\nMCのアイドルグループと対決する予定ですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the day of the show‚ we'll be competing against\nthe MC idol group at a special set on the beach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1649660904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "砂浜はスタジオと勝手が違いますし\nましてや生放送で、何が起こるか分かりませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The beach is different from the studio‚\nand it's a live broadcast‚ so anything could happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5982994238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "あらかじめ現場を見て、対策を練っておきたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see the site in advance and prepare accordingly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2974592368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……さすがmihoさん\nバラエティ番組でも、本気で勝ちにいくつもりですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…As expected of miho-san.\nYou're determined to win‚ even in a variety show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}